<a id=3D"CFtofract"></a>
<h3 id=3D"section3.1">3.1      By "unfolding" the CF  from the right
</h3>
The natural way is just to "fold" the continued fraction from the right-han=
d end, simplifying each part in turn:<br>

<div align=3D"center">

