Here is another example for =E2=88=9A6.
<div class=3D"indent m">
=E2=88=9A6 =3D 2 + x<br>
6 =3D (2 + x)<sup>2</sup> =3D 4 + 4x + x<sup>2</sup><br>
2 =3D 4x + x<sup>2</sup> =3D x(4 + x)<br>
