The first takes only 10 terms to find Pi to 4dps and 16 terms to find 10dps
but the second takes 33 terms (ending with a 6 as a denominator) to find 4d=
ps and even after 1000 terms only has only=20
9 dps accuracy.<p>
In 1748 Euler found these:
</p><div class=3D"center">
<table class=3D"m fracTBL1 centerPage">
